{"tid":1204411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】向美國政府請願要求對推行逃犯條例之香港官員作出制裁","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:13:36.000Z","uid":258326,"like":297,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"b7690bd9ea5d6192b929f7df9e349c1869991353","tid":1204411,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fimpose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiZIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=e9a7535a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/impose-sanctions-upon-hong-kong-officials-who-are-acting-against-american-interests</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Impose sanctions upon Hong Kong officials who are acting against American interests.</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong government is on the verge of passing an extradition bill. If succeeds, US citizens travelling to Hong Kong would be at risk of being extradited to the Mainland China for crimes occurred there from the indefinite past, or &lsquo;crimes&rsquo; fabricated by the PRC government to advance its political interests. In light of the ongoing trade war and past abductions of foreign citizens by Chinese agents, the risk facing US interests there is both tangible and unacceptable. We petition for the US Government to impose sanction against the Hong Kong politicians who push for this bills, and any individuals residing in the US with known ties to them.<br />\n<br />\n簡譯：<br />\n<strong>要求對推行逃犯條例之香港官員作出制裁</strong><br />\n香港政府即將通過一項引渡條例。如果成功，到香港旅遊之美國公民將面對被引渡至中國的風險，理因可以是無限過去時所犯下的罪行，或中國政府所炮製的「罪行」。有鑑於持續的貿易戰以及中國特工過往曾在港抓獲外國公民，美國在港利益面對的風險是實在且無法接受的。我們請願要求美國政府對那些推動這條法案的香港政要，以及任何身居美國並與其有聯繫的人等，實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟，做嘢！</span></span>"},{"pid":"a4900de274b5b99f3f8f475cb98faf0b9f9712cd","tid":1204411,"uid":24133,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"[緊急] 612 組織BC及BNO人到英領遞交聯署信<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ccda57c7eb7f55af3ff093fd476b90cad5b7ba6","tid":1204411,"uid":156868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5a943317cde0e3479e68da8ab73f983ec3f83a","tid":1204411,"uid":258326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:08:19.000Z","msg":"自push"},{"pid":"b31501d18ce22d465f330d5435d1249334aa72a6","tid":1204411,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:33.000Z","msg":"[反送中] 二讀、全體審議及三讀 時間表及詳情<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1204351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1204351</a>"},{"pid":"591782604009d80556651f2ab933bb0d38f202b3","tid":1204411,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557bc689cc30eb42160aefd4a56b701629d42a5a","tid":1204411,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"Done"},{"pid":"03565f5e86055a7e802fd0d90c7cd5d7a15ab2b7","tid":1204411,"uid":4739,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6fwaT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=